    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打倒大量怪兽，用必杀技挑战BOSS吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Gladius Survivors是一款不断升级，使用必杀技挑战强大怪兽的爽快动作、类生存者游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将作为政府雇佣的【Rouge】，通过突然出现在现代社会的【Gate】进入异世界、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作政府开发的系统【Gladius】来控制特殊的剑打倒怪兽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你每次只能在异世界里存在20分钟。尽可能地获得更多地【结晶】吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue Gladius Survivors的玩法：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打倒大量怪兽！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231490/extras/4d5197a5b183004315d5ecb9fb9cdee6.poster.avif?t=1741137677\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231490/extras/4d5197a5b183004315d5ecb9fb9cdee6.webm?t=1741137677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Rogue Gladius Survivors里打倒敌人可以获得剑、指挥剑可以放出强力的【必杀技】。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >锻炼剑释放出最强的必杀技！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231490/extras/980e1757509bd60a6c457f644a28dbd4.avif?t=1741137677\" width=600 height=338 /></span>通过打倒怪兽获得的【魔石】来锻炼剑，从而升级【必殺技】。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >变强后、可以挑战中BOSS，大BOSS。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地图来挑战中BOSS，大BOSS吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231490/extras/ac8525e41492693cb55bfb4882c9e52a.poster.avif?t=1741137677\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231490/extras/ac8525e41492693cb55bfb4882c9e52a.webm?t=1741137677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>如果能找到坐镇在地图中的中BOSS的话说不定就是获得大量道具的机会哦！关卡最后还会出现巨大BOSS！</p>",
